title: Fagor Futuro Pressure Cookers
description:
For additional information on the product featured, please visit: http://www.surlatable.com/product/PRO-6913/Fagor+Futuro+Pressure+Cookers

The ultimate in advanced pressure cookers, the Futuro comes with two short handles for easy storage, an automatic-locking lid for added convenience, an easy-cleaning valve, a steamer basket that doubles as a food grater, and a Tastefully Under Pressure cookbook with over 90 delicious recipes.
